---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>CNN Detection - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">CNN-Based Robotic Object Detection</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        This undergraduate research project focused on robotic perception and visual navigation integration, improving detection performance and connecting object recognition with robotics deployment scenarios.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200">
        <img src="/assets/projects/cnn-detection.png" alt="CNN-based robotic object detection" class="w-full object-cover" />
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
